extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic API to get and process sensors data from purpleair.com and thingspeak.com.

  h1 Dynamic contents

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The API has the following records:

    ul
      li #[strong Total Number Of Sensors:] !{data.length}
      li #[strong Total Number Of Active Sensors:] !{data.length}
      li #[strong List Of The Sensors:] !{data}

